265
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:13,560
Woi, bisinglah!

266
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:16,070
Korang tu dah bukan budak-budak lagi.

267
00:19:16,510 --> 00:19:18,370
Di tempat mandi awam jangan buat bisinglah.

268
00:19:18,810 --> 00:19:20,010
Draken.

269
